1.title: How to print
1.content: How to print . To print a page of this website it is suggested to enable the reader before printing it . Safari: Shift+CMD+R | Firefox Widnows: CTRL+Alt+R | Mac OS: CMD+Alt+R | . | Chrome (should work directly with print) | .
